      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Deews/ mehs eſſam ar\nuhſahm Aufim to dſrdejschi/\nuhſu Tehwi irr muhs to tei-\nſchi/ tu eſſi weenu Darbu dar-\njs wiꞥnu Laika fenn Deenas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu eſſi ar tawu Rohſu\nohſ Pagans isdsinits/ bet\noinaus eſſi tu debſtijs/ tu eſſi\nahs Tantas mohzijs/ bet win-\nns eſſi tu iſplattijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tee ne irr to Semni\nur fawu Sohbinn eemantoj-\nhi/ un winnu Efkins teem ne\nt palihdſeis/ bet tawa labba\nRohka/ un taws Efkins/ un ta-\nva Waiga Gaischums/ jo tew\nija labs Prahts pee teem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu eſſi tas pats ak Deews!\nnans Rehninsch/ pawehli ka Jeh-\nabain tohp palihdſehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ar tew gribbain mehs fa-\nvus Eenaidneekus * fagransiht/\neſſch tawa Wahrdã gribbain\nnehs famiht/ kas prett muhs\nelfahs.\n* Eebr: Wall: Nobaddiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo es ne zerreju us man-\nu Stohpu/ un mans Schbins\nnan ne warr palihdſeht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tu iſglabb muhs no\nnhſeim Prettineekeem/ un\ntu leez muhtus Eenaidneekus\nRauna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eeksch Deewa leeſijancees\nanru Deenu/ un patezaim ta-\nwam Wahrdam muhschtgi /\nSela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet nu atſtuut tu muhs/\nun darri muhs Rauna/ un ne iſ-\neti starp muhsu Karra-Spehku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu dsenn muhs atpak-\nkaz preekſch muhſeem Prettince-\nkeem/ ka muhsu Eenaidneeki\nmuhs fawa Preekſcha aplaupa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu nodohd muhs ka N-\nwis par Barribu/ un iſkaift\nmuhs starp teem Paganceem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu pahrdohd tawus Can. r.\ndis welts/ un ne spreed preekſch so\nwinneem ne kahdu Maksu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu eezell muhs muhſeem\nKaimineein par Apſimeekſi/ par\nNeewatchanu un Apniehdifcha-\nnu teem/ kas apfahrt mums irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu darri muhs par tak-\nkamu Wahrdũ starp teem Pa-\nganceem/ ka tahs Tantas pahr\nmums to Galwn kratta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mans Kanns irr ikdee-\nnas man klaht/ un ta Apkauno-\nſchana apklaibj mannũ Waigu/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "To Mehdiſajn un Sat-\nmotaju Walledas pehz/ to Ee-\nnaidneeku un Atreebeju deht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas wits mums irr uſ-\ngahjis/ tatschu mehs tewis ne\ncſam aismirſuschi/ nedg wiltigi\nprett tawu Derribu darriſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Muhsu Sirđs ne irr at-\npakat greesuſees/ nedg muhsu\nSohti no taweem Zelſteem iſ-\ntihduschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka tu muhs ta fatreez\nstarp teem Puheem/ un apklaibj\nmuhs ar Nahwes Ehnn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Buhtum mehs muhsu\nDeewa Wahrdũ aismirtuschi/\nun muhsas Rohkas us kahdu\ntwechu Deewu iſplattijschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Neggi to Deews warretu\n"
    }
  ],
